Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman sekelasku, Ishikawa, adalah vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu untuk artikel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Surat Kabar Kashinoki, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia keren, misterius,\Ndan selalu menjadi pusat perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah semua orang terlalu menatap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami ingin kalian bersikap sealami mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cobalah untuk tidak memperhatikan kamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juru Kamera! Apakah kau\Nmemotret Ishikawa barusan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waspadalah! Tidak pernah ada momen\Nsaat dia tidak fotogenik!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau salinan fotonya nanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sedang ada kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau Ishikawa\Nmenjawab pertanyaan selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus sekali, Pak Kishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa duduk sekarang, Henmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti bisa, Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersikaplah yang alami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Kalian membuatku\Nsulit berkonsentrasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tegang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tidak bercanda saat mengatakan\Ningin menjadi dekat dan akrab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh menakjubkan surat kabar lokal\Nsampai datang ke sekolah untuk meliputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misuzu mengizinkan mereka\Nkarena menurutnya itu seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa! Masih ada wawancara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori! Kau bisa makan siang tanpa aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai nanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah menunggumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menyetujui ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku Ishikawa Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harap ini akan menjadi\Nwawancara yang baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menggemaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Otori, di mana Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Otori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Luna tidak ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia, ada wawancara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita mulai, Ishikawa Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masyarakat membicarakanmu\Nsebagai Nona Vampir Kecil yang cantik!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami ingin mengajukan\Nbeberapa pertanyaan mengenai hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, sebenarnya\Napa yang mereka katakan tentangku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ini tentang\Naku adalah vampir yang berkelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama-tama, kau membantu\Nseorang wanita tua menyeberang jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang aku dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna memakai payung!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuatku terlihat seperti vampir, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana datangnya angin itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Tunggu, aku tidak bisa turun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna! Lepaskan payungnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin, itu berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menyebutnya Insiden\NKucing Terbang Istimewa Kashinokidai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara soal ketinggian, ada juga ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat! Kucing itu terjebak di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau aman sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang, aku akan membantumu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamatkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, jangan melihat ke bawah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku segera ke sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang, ambil bantal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Polisi! Panggil polisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua ini tentang\Naku mempermalukan diriku sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Menurutku itu menghangatkan hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tampak sangat dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misuzu… Direktur…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu baik padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran\Napa yang mereka tanyakan kepadanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal-hal seperti apa yang dia lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana cara dia\Nmenghabiskan waktu di rumah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku ingin tahu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga punya pertanyaan untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, mereka bilang vampir tidak bisa\Nberada di bawah sinar matahari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana dia bisa mengatasi\Ngelombang panas yang akan datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terangnya! Panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia pernah bilang\Ndia baik-baik saja dengan tabir surya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sinar matahari bukan kelemahannya\Npadahal dia vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia menderita\Njika berjalan di bawah hujan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar-benar kelemahannya, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dipikir-pikir...\NAku tidak pernah tahu itu tentang dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu! Kita harus membuat\Ngrup obrolan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begitu\Nkita selalu bisa membicarakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, bagaimana cara membuatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh... hah? Apakah itu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan itu kepadaku!\NAku akan melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saja pertanyaan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan mengirimkan artikelnya\Nkalau sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terakhir, kami ingin foto kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh... tentang foto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya aku menyebutkannya lebih awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir tidak terlihat di foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu salah satunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak memiliki bayangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena tidak mencari tahu\Nterlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi berarti kita harus\Nmemikirkan sesuatu selain foto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengasuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bisa membagikan\Nsemua pengamatan kalian di obrolan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Boleh aku mulai lebih dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menggemaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, itu benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya!\NGigitannya sangat menyakitkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengalaman bisa berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyukai makanan manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, dia makan apa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia makan bawang putih hitam baru-baru ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya itu sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, halo? Vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia atletis dan cerdas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terlihat mengantuk di pagi hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia lebih kuat dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna benar-benar menggemaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit kupercaya dia pernah\Nmenjalani kehidupan yang penuh bahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencoba menanyainya\Ntentang semua ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori, apakah kau\Nmenjadi orang yang berbeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya Luna yang berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menjadi lebih ceria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa memakai pita?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku adalah hadiahnya untuk sisa hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Wah, wah!\N- Manisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Semoga aku tidak terbawa suasana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengadakan percakapan\Ntanpa melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku masih gugup bahkan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku merasa senang\Nberbicara dengan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini juga berkat Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani sekali kau bilang begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori, aku lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali, Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana wawancaranya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh... ada masalah dengan foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Foto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak terlihat di foto\Nkarena aku adalah vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung aku punya gambar dari Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gambar dari hari ulang tahunmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena menggunakannya tanpa izin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak keberatan, hanya saja...\Nkau yakin ingin menampilkannya di koran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Soalnya itu sangat lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya! Apa maksudnya "pengasuh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, apa yang kalian bertiga bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami senang mengetahui\Nlebih banyak hal tentang dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Kau panas sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh suatu hal yang berani\Nuntuk dikatakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Bisakah aku menggunakan gambar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini. Aku menggunakannya\Nsebagai ikon profilku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami ingin meminta izinmu\Nuntuk menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan gunakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna, kau sudah berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja! Aku berusaha\Nuntuk menjadi lebih seperti vampir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Misuzu, teman ibumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk memberimu hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Vampir Selalu Sempurna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menjadi\Nvampir yang keren dan misterius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, meniru tokoh utama wanita di manga\Nbisa membuatnya meninggalkan rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna selalu pemalu di dekat orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tumbuh menjadi gadis manis, Shirayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah memikirkan\Napa yang akan kau gambar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencoba menggambar beberapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Itu cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakaktua dan Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku semuanya bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah tepatnya\Nyang Kusunoki peringatkan kepadamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu memperlakukannya seperti bayi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, semuanya memerlukan latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, aku bisa mengerti\Nkau selalu berusaha yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak sedih...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya. Ishikawa, aku butuh bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang subjek karyaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa mendapatkan gambaran\Nyang jelas dari foto referensi saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang berpikir untuk berkunjung\Nke sebuah lokasi dan membuat sketsanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin setelah ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ide bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau membicarakan hal ini denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau menikmati\Nliburan tahunan ke luar negeri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendapat kesan\Nkau mengenal banyak tujuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?! Sebaliknya,\Naku belum pernah jalan-jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku cepat sekali merasa lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku mencari makanan enak\Nke mana pun aku pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sendiri kedengarannya menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ada yang bisa memberiku nutrisi\Nkecuali darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggaplah kita melakukan\Nperjalanan jarak jauh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan jadi seperti ini\Nsaat kita kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamasya kami sebelumnya\Ndi lingkungan dekat sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau udon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalan-jalan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau rutin pergi\Nke berbagai tempat untuk menggambar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak secara rutin,\Ntapi kurasa aku cukup sering melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Aku ingin sekali melihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana gambarmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak akan menemukannya di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dipikir-pikir, aku belum pernah\Nmelihat gambarmu yang lengkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku membawa pulang semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, semuanya ada di rumahmu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa akan berkunjung ke rumahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah sampai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumahmu adalah toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mengelola bisnis kecil, tapi ini juga\Ntempat pembuatan sake lokal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat! Aku akan memberi tahu\NIbu dan Ayah untuk berkunjung!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah orang tuamu juga vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Mereka suka alkohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada gambaran umum\Nvampir memegang gelas anggur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau menunggu di sini sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang... Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di rumah, Tatsuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu harus mengantar sesuatu.\NJaga toko, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu berangkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menakjubkan! Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat semua sake itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nih, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami... kehabisan teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sup miso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami selalu punya miso\Ndan kecap di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ini yang bisa aku sajikan\Ndalam waktu singkat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan merasa tidak enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harum sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih untuk supnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti darahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darahku rasa sup miso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin sekali\Nmakan sup miso ini tiap hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan hidup dari darahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan sup miso sebagai pendampingnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang aku sebut kemewahan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu milikmu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore! Ada begitu banyak gambar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Tidak ada yang menarik\Nyang bisa dilihat di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, di mana ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pantai yang kami kunjungi tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegunungan yang sedikit lebih jauh\Ndari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat gambarmu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatku merasa\Nbenar-benar pergi ke tempat-tempat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu luar biasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah entah itu pantai\Natau pegunungan. Kau bisa memilihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan puas hanya dengan melihat.\NKita akan pergi bersama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ma-Maksudmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kita berdua?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Berdua?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em... Aku pikir ada lebih dari satu donor\Nakan mengurangi bebanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau perlu lebih banyak latihan lebih dulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena Kusunoki merasa\Ngigitanmu menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berusaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ingin sekali\Npergi jalan-jalan bersamamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Semangat, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita coba saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin tidak sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan waktu yang tepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku waktu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencetaknya di kaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya\Ndi Li'l Miss Vampire Can't Suck Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Nona Vampir Kecil dan Baju Renang".
